<L>__{interior radio station day}
<A>__{debi flips on the "on air" switch and prepares to speak into the microphone. martin walks in. debi sees him. they stare at each other. the song ends. dead air. after a moment...}
<C>__{debi}
<P>__{(on air, groping)}
<D>__{wrfn playing all vinyl, all the time. oldies from the eighties. that was ah... the specials. doing... one of their songs...}
